raw_input.text:
The Projects has engaged Sarah Chen to present support for the Premium fashion Series on behalf of Style Studio. As consumers increasingly seek sustainable products, Australians are seeking better fashion solutions. As the initiative's brand partner, Sarah Chen will deliver key messages across media and social channels. This campaign reinforces the brand's leadership in fashion.

INFLUENCER AGREEMENT

This agreement is between Style Studio and the Influencer for Style Studio Wardrobe Campaign 2025.

COMMERCIAL TERMS:
- Total Fee: $11,431 AUD (inclusive of GST)
- Payment Terms: Net 30 days from invoice date
- Invoice Requirements: Tax invoice required upon completion

DELIVERABLES:
- 1 x Instagram posts

TERMS AND CONDITIONS:
- Engagement Period: 3 months
- Exclusivity Period: 6 weeks
- Territory: Australia
- Usage Rights: 18 months from campaign launch
- Content Rights: Style Studio retains full commercial rights

COMPLIANCE:
- All content must comply with ACMA guidelines and ASA codes
- Content is subject to client approval before publication
- Disclosure requirements must be met per ACCC guidelines

LEGAL:
This agreement is governed by Australian law and subject to the jurisdiction of Australian courts.

Agreed terms are subject to final contract execution.
